==English==

===Etymology===
[[earth]] + [[worm]]

===Noun===
'''earthworm'''
# A [[worm]] that lives in the [[ground]].
# A disparaging reference to a [[person]], particularly one who [[grovel]]s.
# A figurative reference to [[death]].

